Welcome to the brand new Smithsonian Channel streaming service. Explore history mystery science and pop culture with more original series and entertaining documentaries than ever before. Enjoy it for free no commitment or cable subscription required or upgrade to Smithsonian Channel Plus to gain access to our deep library of nonfiction entertainment including full seasons of our most popular series such as Aerial America America in Color and Air Disasters.
